<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Zend_XmlRpc_Server sends HTTP header Content-Type: application/xml, but in  <a href="">www.xmlrpc.com/spec</a>" rel="nofollow"&gt;XML-RPC spec I see responce example with Content-Type: text/xml. So, Zend XML-RPC client is not compatible with XML-RPC spec. Moreover it dosn't work with some XML-RPC clients (Ruby XML-RPC for example).</p>

